                      </a>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </article>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- About the Author Box -->
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16 lg:mt-24">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-12 border border-primary/10 shadow-lg">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
              <div class="md:w-1/3 flex-shrink-0">
                <img
                  src="/pictures/AmandaLiczner.jpg"
                  alt="Dr. Amanda Liczner, bumble bee ecologist and pollinator colouring book author"
                  class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-md"
                  loading="lazy"
                  width="300"
                  height="300"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="md:w-2/3">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium mb-4">
                  <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                    About the Author
                  </span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                  <strong>Dr. Amanda Liczner</strong> is a conservation biologist specializing in bumble bee ecology.
                  She holds a PhD in Biology from York University and currently conducts leading research
                 on pollinator ecology and animal movement across North America. 
                </p>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                  Her research has been published in leading scientific journals, and she's dedicated to making
                  pollinator science accessible to all ages through education and art.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                  <a
                    href="/experience"
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-white rounded-xl hover:bg-secondary transition-colors"
                  >
                    View Research Experience
                  </a>
                  <a
                    href="/skills-education"
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-secondary text-neutral-700 rounded-xl hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors"
                  >
                    Education & Expertise
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Educational Content Section for SEO -->
